10:22.833 --> 10:24.041
Let me ask you,

10:25.791 --> 10:28.291
do you remember where you proposed to me?

10:28.791 --> 10:29.875
And where we went for our honeymoon?

10:29.875 --> 10:30.000
I proposed to you on the rooftop.

10:30.000 --> 10:31.791
I proposed to you on the rooftop.

10:33.083 --> 10:34.708
We were poor then

10:35.125 --> 10:36.833
