13:17.916 --> 13:19.625
I was about to order delivery.

13:22.875 --> 13:24.250
I brought food for you,

13:25.291 --> 13:26.000
medicine,

13:26.333 --> 13:27.083
books,

13:27.333 --> 13:28.458
and some clean clothes.

13:28.583 --> 13:29.416
Thanks.

13:29.791 --> 13:30.000
I saw her.

13:30.000 --> 13:30.833
I saw her.

13:31.333 --> 13:32.916
She's fine, don't worry.

13:40.791 --> 13:41.500
Hello?

13:42.791 --> 13:43.791
Huilan

13:46.583 --> 13:48.375
I just wanted him to know I'm OK.

13:54.958 --> 13:56.083
If you do this,

13:56.166 --> 13:57.625
then what's the point of hiding?

14:21.041 --> 14:22.250
You're right.

14:27.333 --> 14:28.833
Thank you for all your help.

14:29.083 --> 14:30.000
But there are some things that

14:30.000 --> 14:30.541
But there are some things that

14:30.625 --> 14:32.666
I have to clear up with him in person.

14:33.125 --> 14:34.083
OK, I'll come with you.

14:34.458 --> 14:35.541
Don't.

14:36.333 --> 14:38.041
I can handle this myself.

15:34.041 --> 15:37.000
You've really mixed my memories up.

15:37.041 --> 15:37.833
Mr. Jiang,

15:37.875 --> 15:39.625
we've all signed confidentiality agreements.

15:39.750 --> 15:41.375
We don't know the contents of your memories.

15:41.416 --> 15:42.416
Which is to say,

15:42.458 --> 15:44.583
we are responsible for safekeeping your memory chip,

15:44.666 --> 15:45.958
but not for its contents.

15:46.458 --> 15:48.083
Well, memories must at least be sequential, right?

15:48.333 --> 15:51.041
They can't just be random fragments with no context.

15:51.125 --> 15:54.166
Didn't I say it takes 3 days to fully restore your memories?

15:54.291 --> 15:57.083
Maybe in a few days, you'll have the context to make sense of it.

15:57.500 --> 15:58.750
Mr. Jiang, how about I...

15:59.541 --> 16:00.000
If it's our problem, we will take responsibility.

16:00.000 --> 16:01.666
If it's our problem, we will take responsibility.

16:01.666 --> 16:04.208
But all your suspicions now have no basis.

16:04.583 --> 16:05.916
It's pure speculation.

16:06.125 --> 16:07.458
I've done my research.

16:07.500 --> 16:09.833
This surgery hasn't been approved in several countries.

16:09.833 --> 16:12.750
That must mean there are problems with it.

16:19.291 --> 16:20.291
Mr. Jiang,

16:20.791 --> 16:22.708
are you familiar with plastic surgery

16:22.791 --> 16:24.583
