16:53.125 --> 16:54.916
it opens another possibility:

16:55.041 --> 16:56.500
helping criminals to hide their identities

16:56.500 --> 16:58.250
and escape the law.

16:59.041 --> 17:00.000
Do you believe this is fair?

17:00.000 --> 17:00.250
Do you believe this is fair?

17:01.666 --> 17:04.375
Our surgery is no different from plastic surgery.

17:04.666 --> 17:06.250
One is for physical defects.

17:06.375 --> 17:08.250
The other is for emotional trauma.

17:08.625 --> 17:11.250
The original motivations of these surgeries are good.

17:11.291 --> 17:14.416
But the key lies in the user's intentions.

17:14.625 --> 17:15.916
What are you saying?

17:17.125 --> 17:18.291
What I'm saying is,

17:18.833 --> 17:21.583
