19:05.916 --> 19:06.583
None of your business.

19:06.625 --> 19:07.250
Sit back down.

19:12.375 --> 19:14.166
But Officer, I know some information.

19:14.375 --> 19:15.583
What do you know?

19:16.416 --> 19:17.250
Tell me.

19:17.666 --> 19:19.083
Well...did this woman

19:19.083 --> 19:21.458
