20:44.708 --> 20:47.791
I can see the killer drown Li Huilan in the bathtub.

20:49.875 --> 20:51.208
You saw that.

20:51.958 --> 20:53.083
I did.

20:54.708 --> 20:55.833
Are you sure?

20:56.833 --> 20:57.916
I saw it with my own eyes.

20:58.083 --> 20:59.375
With your own eyes.

21:00.125 --> 21:01.500
In my memories.

21:02.791 --> 21:03.791
OK bigshot author,

21:04.541 --> 21:06.416
please stop wasting our time.

21:06.583 --> 21:08.625
If you need inspiration, go watch the news.

21:08.875 --> 21:10.291
I'm telling the truth!

21:13.916 --> 21:15.041
Take a break.

21:17.291 --> 21:18.916
Wait for your family to come post bail.

21:19.625 --> 21:21.625
Why won't you believe me?

21:21.750 --> 21:23.541
It's a big greenhouse, should be easy to spot.

21:23.666 --> 21:24.375
OK.

21:25.416 --> 21:26.958
Also there's a number of wood carvings inside.

21:27.125 --> 21:28.833
One is unfinished.

21:31.041 --> 21:34.041
You can investigate Huilan's close friends.

21:34.625 --> 21:35.625
Mr. Jiang,

21:35.625 --> 21:37.625
you really are an excellent storyteller.

21:54.583 --> 21:56.041
Hello, is this the police?

21:57.541 --> 21:58.791
I'm at Seawall Village, Twenty...

