22:09.875 --> 22:11.125
Honey, I was wrong.

22:11.375 --> 22:12.500
Come back home.

22:13.458 --> 22:14.291
Honey,

22:14.416 --> 22:16.000
I'm holding a knife,

22:16.416 --> 22:17.916
