Sister,

22:37.375 --> 22:38.333
Sister,

22:38.625 --> 22:40.125
Are you sure?

22:45.000 --> 22:45.958
Mom,

22:46.833 --> 22:48.791
I know I've been bad.

22:49.333 --> 22:51.458
I will change.

22:56.625 --> 22:57.541
Mom.

