23:30.000 --> 23:31.083
Please slow down.

23:33.916 --> 23:34.666
I'm begging you.

23:34.666 --> 23:35.875
I was wrong, I'm sorry.

23:35.916 --> 23:36.625
Let him off the car.

23:36.625 --> 23:38.041
At least let him off the car.

23:38.666 --> 23:39.708
Car! Car!

23:40.541 --> 23:42.500
-Will you listen to me? -I will, I will.

23:42.500 --> 23:43.958
Yes, yes, whatever you say.

24:04.833 --> 24:06.625
You treated me like garbage.

24:06.708 --> 24:08.083
You left me no choice.

24:09.250 --> 24:10.375
No choice!

24:10.500 --> 24:11.541
No choice!

24:11.708 --> 24:13.458
Today, in front of your family,

24:13.500 --> 24:14.708
in front him,

24:14.750 --> 24:16.833
